<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HRManagment - Bienvenido</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .welcome-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="welcome-container">
        <h1>HRManagment</h1>
        <p>Bienvenido a HRManagment, la solución integral para la gestión de contrataciones y vacaciones de empleados.</p>
        <p>Optimiza tus procesos de recursos humanos de manera eficiente y efectiva.</p>
        <a href="dashboard.html" class="btn">Empezar</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
